I. A Suppoſition, (that Chriſtian Brethren may be overtaken in ſuch Faults as render them like Members out of joynt, in the Body of Chriſt, to which they belong: and ſo need (to prevent their farther Corruption, and danger of becoming Gangrened, and in the Iſſue, cut off) the charitable Endeavours of their Fellows to ſet them in Joynt again.) For ſo the Word (
                  〈 in non-Latin alphabet 〉
               ) which we render (reſtore,) does import.

1. The Perſons who are thus to endeavour the Offenders Reſtitution, are here called (
